          <title>
            <string language="en">The Battle of Antietam/Sharpsburg -- Special Subjects</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Die Schlacht von Antietam/Sharpsburg -- spezielle 
Themen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La bataille d'Antietam/Sharpsburg -- sujets

            <string language="x-mt-pt">A batalha de Antietam/Sharpsburg -- assuntos

especiales</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">shows the kinds of artillery and battle tactics used at Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) and provides information on General Robert Lee, General George McClellan, Clara Barton, and more.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">zeigt die Arten der Artillerie- und 
Schlachttaktiken, die bei Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) verwendet 
werden und stellt Informationen auf General Robert Lee, General George
McClellan, Clara Barton und mehr zur Verfügung.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">montre les genres de tactique d'artillerie et de 
bataille utilisée chez Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) et fournit des
informations sur le Général Robert Lee, George général 
McClellan, Clara Barton, et plus.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">mostra os tipos das táticas da artilharia e da 
batalha usadas em Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) e fornece a 
informação no general Robert Lee, general George McClellan, Clara 
Barton, e mais.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">mostra i generi di tattiche di battaglia e 
dell'artiglieria usate a Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) e fornisce le
informazioni sul General Robert Lee, il General George McClellan, 
Clara Barton e più.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εμφανίζει τα είδη τακτικής πυροβολικού και μάχης που 
χρησιμοποιείται σε Antietam (Sharpsburg, Μέρυλαντ) και 
παρέχει τις πληροφορίες για το στρατηγό Robert Lee, 
στρατηγός George McClellan, Κλάρα Barton, και 
περισσότεροι.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">muestra las clases de táctica de la artillería y 
de la batalla usadas en Antietam (Sharpsburg, Maryland) y proporciona 
a la información en general Roberto Lee, general George McClellan, 
Clara Barton, y más.</string>
